1
00:00:00,750 --> 00:00:04,360
Want to make your accessibility statement page easier for your customers to find?

2
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:09,820
In this video, I'll show you exactly how to add a page to your Shopify menu.

3
00:00:09,820 --> 00:00:12,180
So your customers can access it effortlessly.

4
00:00:12,180 --> 00:00:17,460
If you're new to Shopify or just getting started, don't worry.

5
00:00:17,460 --> 00:00:19,260
I'll walk you through each step clearly.

6
00:00:19,260 --> 00:00:22,860
By the end of this video, you'll know how to link any page to your store's navigation.

7
00:00:23,380 --> 00:00:25,720
Making browsing intuitive for everyone.

8
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:29,910
Step 1: From your Shopify dashboard, click on content.

9
00:00:29,910 --> 00:00:33,700
Then select menus, this is where you manage all your store's menus.

10
00:00:33,960 --> 00:00:35,010
Step 2:

11
00:00:35,010 --> 00:00:36,460
Choose the menu you want to edit.

12
00:00:36,460 --> 00:00:41,200
For this video, we'll use the footer menu which appears at the bottom of your store.

13
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,470
Click on it to see the existing menu items.

14
00:00:43,470 --> 00:00:44,790
Step 3:

15
00:00:44,790 --> 00:00:46,260
Click on Add menu item.

16
00:00:46,550 --> 00:00:50,000
Enter the name of the new item, for example, accessibility statement.

17
00:00:50,470 --> 00:00:53,490
Step 4: Link this menu item to the page you want it to lead to.

18
00:00:53,880 --> 00:00:58,040
Since this is an accessibility statement, select your accessibility statement page.

19
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:59,380
Step 5:

20
00:00:59,570 --> 01:01:20,530
Click save to update the menu. Step 6: Go to your online store and click up here to view your store, you'll see the accessibility statement page successfully added to your footer menu, ready for your customers to access easily.

21
01:01:20,530 --> 01:01:22,960
Now your Shopify menu is updated.

22
01:01:22,960 --> 01:01:25,720
And your customers can navigate your store more easily.

23
01:01:26,380 --> 01:01:29,780
Don't forget to try it yourself and make your store even more user friendly.